records.name: Taj Coral Reef Resort & Spa,maldives - Premium All Inclusive With Free Transfers

descriptions.direction: Located in Hembadhu Island, Taj Coral Reef Resort & Spa Maldives – A Premium All Inclusive Resort is on a private beach. Madivaru Beyru Dive Site and Baros Marine Center are worth checking out if an activity is on the agenda, while those wishing to experience the area's natural beauty can explore Vabbininfaru Beach and Angsana Beach. Looking to get your feet wet? Windsurfing and swimming adventures can be found near the property.
descriptions.general: Taj Coral Reef Resort and Spa has all the exotic ocean views and dramatic sunsets you need for the perfect tropical holiday. The resort is a diver's dream, but also for those who prefer to stay on land, the view of the lagoon dotted with water villas is mesmerising. Located in North Male atoll, at Hembadhoo island, by the beach, 30 km from Thulusdhoo island (by boat), 35 km from Velena international airport (by boat) and 40 km from Male center (by boat). The resort also offers island buyout for guests looking for an exclusive resort experience. Price shown does NOT include arrival and return transfer, but is compulsory to book. You are required to book the appropriate transfer and supply all the required transfer information. Hotel booking is not regarded as confirmed until the transfer booking has been completed. Facilities and services include restaurant, bar, lounge, garden, swimming pool, gym, spa (extra charge), jacuzzi, wireless Internet access and 24-hour reception. Rooms measuring 58 m², feature telephone, TV, safe, air conditioning, wireless Internet access, coffee/tea maker, dinning area, balcony/terrace, bathrobes, slippers, and hairdryer. Bathrooms for Superior & Deluxe beach villa features well-ventilated, four-fixture bathrooms with grab bars and outdoor shower illuminated by natural light. Nirvana Presidential Suite measuring 215 m², also feature private pool and living room. IMPORTANT NOTE: Starting 15th August 2022, all villas in the resort are strict non-smoking zones. This decision was prompted by concern for the safety of guests. Our sustainably-designed villas have several combustible elements like the open wooden deck flooring and dried coconut leaf thatches . All public areas of the resort continue to be open for smoking, including restaurants. We look forward to this safety measure being communicated to prospective guests and their enthusiastic participation in our collective commitment to responsible and ethical tourism. Check-in time: 15:00 Check-out time: 12:00 Please note that some of the above facilities may be closed due to weather/seasonal conditions. Please note all villas in the resort are strict non-smoking zones. ALL-INCLUSIVE MEALS: Breakfast – 0700 to 1000 hours Lunch 3 course meal – 1200 to 1430 hours Dinner 3 course meal – 1900 to 2130 hours Bar – 1100 to 0000 hours Mediterranean lunch 3 course meal – 1200 to 1430 hours Dinner 3 course meal – 1900 to 2130 hours (prior reservations) Address: North Male Atoll, Male, North Central Province, Maldives.
